{"type": "article", "id": 17484, "title": "水泥洗手池", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-13T06:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122432vBSXaUIFRlZKP2J5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t韩国的设计工作室 Miicon 擅长用水泥和陶瓷做设计材料，这个用 UHPC（高性能混凝土）做的洗手池有一种特别的柔和感。细看时能看到自然的气孔，没有太深的厚度，却恰好反射出室内的照明，有一种厚重原始的典雅，是有温度的极简风。<a href=\"http://www.miicon.co.kr/product/detail.html?product_no=28&amp;cate_no=1&amp;display_group=2\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144603sR1maAXqyWvn02CK.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144605wXRqJPeF2jVY8oZL.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144605MNUxSQHW9pbzdh1A.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144607Nnuf4cZhvAXSmkzD.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}